The United States (US) Mission in Nigeria has sent in a congratulatory message to Wizkid and Burna Boy on their first-ever Grammy award wins. Wizkid and Burna Boy were announced winners of the Grammy awards in their respective categories on Sunday. In a recent tweet, the United States Mission said: “Congratulations to Nigeria’s two #GRAMMYs winners: @wizkidayo -Best Music Video & @burnaboy -Best Global Music Album.”